{"tid":1583564,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"話說頭先10點鳩叫","createTime":"2019-09-20T16:09:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:30:18.000Z","uid":225285,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f6f0acfaa45c79b564e718cf498ab2ccc74dcea6","tid":1583564,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:09:32.000Z","msg":"是咁的，頭先10點鳩叫嗰陣，有一對大陸口音藍屍廢老叫我地唔好嘈<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，之前已經話我地係曱甴，同係咁影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，於是乎我地就越叫越大聲，咁最近我就買咗鐳射筆，諗住拎嚟玩下<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點知玩咗一陣佢就縮返入去，大家以後可以試下咁做，啲藍絲淨係識欺善怕惡<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />見到鐳射筆驚到要偷偷地地拎部電話喺窗邊影相，連望都唔夠膽望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />以後佢一出嚟我就咁做，唔知我會唔會比人告藏有攻擊性武器呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"428216ac0eba963de1c0df42bc012fe7bc5c0e33","tid":1583564,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:09:46.000Z","msg":"光復香港，"},{"pid":"c5473a203d69648bbb9e9627aae077391656ec06","tid":1583564,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:09:58.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，"},{"pid":"77c5d27e620aec07ca535c377eb0b8b700e71a3f","tid":1583564,"uid":225285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:10:24.000Z","msg":"香港人加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2769c2cf68ae822a094a17f43d02d29ac29adda0","tid":1583564,"uid":305536,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-20T16:12:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">割蓆宣言 - 幫手翻譯, 做文宣圖<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kMrteqX\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kMrteqX</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">[新行動]</span> [增加國際輿論] 推到<span